{"tid":1240508,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國領事館請願 - 香港人權與民主法案","createTime":"2019-06-18T11:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T11:12:23.000Z","uid":258153,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"78904c4c672dac394c4a0c34ea6a4b98bb121865","tid":1240508,"uid":258153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rq4qqv2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frq4qqv2.png&h=3119ee9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ic7DQ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ic7DQ4.png&h=09a7988b&s={SIZE}\" />我們是「反送中」的地區工作者和基督徒，訴求包括: 撤回「引渡修例」、不檢控「反送中運動」市民、取消定性暴動、引用權力及特權法，調查警方濫用暴力。<br />\n<br />\n我們由 4/6/2018 發起《香港人權與民主法案》聯署，已超過12.5 萬人聯署（截至18/6/2019 )，我們在2019年6月18日把上述聯署交給美國領事館。呼籲美國政府儘快制定法案，保障香港人權，制裁違反人權的官員和議員包括，凍結海外資產、限制入境、每年發表香港人權報告。<br />\n<br />\n我們認為「引渡條例」嚴重破壞一國兩制，本地立法和司法機構無權對中央的「引渡」要求把關，變相實行中國法律，接受沒有司法獨立政權的審判，嚴重損害基本人權。因此，我們希望美國政府制定法案，制裁違反人權的官員。<br />\n<br />\n全球聯署「香港人權與民主法案」，呼籲國際社會立法，持續監察和制裁共匪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/CT2GM4YV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2FCT2GM4YV&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwqxOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=5475f7c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/CT2GM4YV</a>"},{"pid":"eacc6f8cfaa19a9d48a0ea5e183ac178516be996","tid":1240508,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9147fbf1d35062d6fa06e8ac068172dfcc8743","tid":1240508,"uid":258153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"更正（4/6/2019）開始聯署"},{"pid":"202991fdb605300977a1cb5c9445b2e0c3d4b053","tid":1240508,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no